-- Bhangui Joins Byron, Morgan Stanley Hires Tom Halton, Vlaad Says
-- B y   K a t i a   D m i t r i e v a
-- 2013-08-16T18:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-16/bhangui-joins-byron-morgan-stanley-hires-tom-halton-vlaad-says.html
Byron Capital Markets Ltd. hired Dev
Bhangui as a research analyst to cover disruptive technologies
from his previous position at Fraser Mackenzie Ltd., according
to Vlaad & Co., a Toronto-based financial services recruiting
firm.  Other moves noted in the “Bill’s Buzz” weekly  newsletter 
include:  * Mario Mendonca, financial services analyst, joined Toronto-Dominion Bank from Canaccord Financial Inc.  * Morgan Stanley hired Tom Halton as an associate in precious
metals research from Raymond James Ltd.  * In Vancouver, Harsh Grewal joined  Scotia Capital , a unit of
the Bank of  Nova Scotia .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katia Dmitrieva in Toronto at 
 edmitrieva1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scanlan at 
 dscanlan@bloomberg.net  